      "value": "<div><div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Prerequisite: 7th level</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>As an action, you gain the ability to see through solid objects to a range of 30 feet. Within that range, you have &amp;Reference[rule=darkvision] if you don't already have it. This special sight lasts for 1 minute or until your @status[concentration] ends (as if you were @status[concentration||concentrating] on a spell). During that time, you perceive objects as ghostly, transparent images.</p><p>Once you use this invocation, you can't use it again until you finish a short or long rest.</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div></div>",
